# Reports & P&L

## Trip P&L filter (`TripPnlFilter.tsx`)

- Trip tab filter lives in `components/reports/TripPnlFilter.tsx` (not inline in `PnlReportView.tsx`).
- Three-row layout: year/month/route/driver → date + clear → blue search button.
- Use **inline styles** for filter controls (not Tailwind) to avoid clipping/visibility issues.
- Pass `drivers={tripsData?.drivers ?? []}` from parent; options populate after first search.
- `onSearch` should call `loadTrips` with override params to avoid stale React state.

## AppShell scrolling

- `main` in `AppShell.tsx` must use `overflow-y-auto`, not `overflow-hidden`.
- Nested `overflow-hidden` on `main` + inner scroll clipped the trip P&L search button.

## P&L API / build

- `/api/*` routes must stay exempt from auth redirect in middleware (JSON, not HTML login page).
- Remove unused imports/vars in `PnlReportView.tsx` before push — ESLint errors block Vercel deploy.

## Driver expenses module

- Voucher UI/print: bilingual A5 pages under `documents/driver-expenses/`.
- Cost reading in reports: actual-first from fees/vouchers (`lib/pnl-report.ts`, `lib/operations-cost.ts`).
